data.name: Detail.Text
data.value:
Thank you for your interest in the Face of Mankind: Fall of the Dominion Open Beta. We’re excited about this next phase of game development and hope you’ll join us.
Open Beta starts on _____. At this point, you’ve installed the major assets of the game such as artwork, textures, sounds and maps. On ____ launch Face of Mankind: Fall of the Dominion from the icon on your desktop. A few last-minute files will be downloaded and you’ll be on your way to creating a character and joining other players in-game.
In the mean time, we invite you to keep up-to-date with our progress on the forums.
